Comment: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.30,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.64,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直响着的沉默的警铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:18.86,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是谁的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.46,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳进去跳进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.82,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起来 破坏掉这无理的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.41,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不开这沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.83,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.16,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到终幕我都要说
